6. WARMUP-1 #6
problem: Warmup-1 > makes10 

"""
Given 2 ints, a and b, return True if one if them is 10 or if their sum is 10. 
makes10(9, 10) → True
makes10(9, 9) → False
makes10(1, 9) → True
"""

FINAL CODE SOLUTION:

def makes10(a, b):
  return ((a==10 or b==10) or (a+b==10))

